The company is also involved in the surface treatment of landing gear components; assembling and installation of aircraft components at customer assembly lines, as well as offers electronic enclosures, heat exchangers, cabinets, and titanium components. It serves commercial and defense sectors of the aerospace industries. It operates in Canada, the United States, the United Kingdom, Rest of Europe, Spain, and internationally.
